话稿。值得注意的是，朱是西着重提到了要加大招商引资力度和发展文旅文创产业。「南阳挣钱襄阳花」引热议，南阳立军令：以壮士断腕精气神优化产业发展 _ 中国政库 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2fb4599622b3690bf2afa9bdb5c90ce5_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/577873287"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIx/GrgcmhlIZNEAMaCDkwNjk3NzU1IL7P850GMAI4lgFAHXIJNTc3ODczMjg3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1673564965.9566703", "card_id": "Q_563871532", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 663}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你悟出一个最大的人生道理是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/563871532"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ix/GrgcmhlIZNEAMaCDg3NTg2ODYwIOaggpsGMAU43QtAHnIJNTYzODcxNTMyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1673564965.9570491", "card_id": "Q_576406653", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 20}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "游戏《鹅鸭杀》怎么玩啊？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我真的太菜了，白混了五十多级 现在到了一个阶段，谁都不信但谁都信，好赖话不分，听发言啥也盘不出还被狼带晕，自己归票全错 玩好人带刀还刀错，不敢选狼，不敢报团 唉，很烦，自己就是个愚鹅，别人觉得很明显我却听不出来盘不出来"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-176f250a56dadba31f0ad536c17ebea8_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/576406653"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ix/GrgcmhlIZNEAMaCDkwMzcxODI3IMKJzZ0GMAM4TkAfcgk1NzY0MDY2NTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed",